description:
#Chinainsights#Chinanews
In early March, the Chinese Communist Party, or CCP held its most important two sessions of the year and it’s been in bad shape since then. The Chinese people are gradually realizing that the world they live in is getting more unreal. In this episode, we'll look at a few clips and side stories of what's been going on in China lately, from the people to the officials. 
First, let's look at a sudden scare when driving in an undersea tunnel.

title: China gets increasingly wacky: From seeping seawater, fires, to iPad for white paper movement...
